    <item>
      <title>顶级银行家通过投奔私人信贷机构来追逐巨额利润</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/private-credit-firms-are-poaching-some-of-wall-street-s-top-loan-bankers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越来越多的杠杆融资银行家跳槽到私人资本公司，以寻求更大的财富和在蓬勃发展的市场中工作的承诺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/private-credit-firms-are-poaching-some-of-wall-street-s-top-loan-bankers</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 04:00:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>PGIM：全球投资者更加关注地缘政治风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-26/pgim-global-investors-more-focused-on-geopolitical-risk-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[PGIM 总裁兼首席执行官 David Hunt 表示，地缘政治仍然是首席信息官和投资者最关心的问题，而非传统的商业周期问题。他在私募股权活动 SuperReturn Asia 的间隙与 Haslinda Amin 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-26/pgim-global-investors-more-focused-on-geopolitical-risk-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 03:58:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国考虑向顶级银行注资 1420 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-26/china-weighing-142b-capital-injection-into-top-banks-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，中国正考虑向其最大的国有银行注入高达 1 万亿元人民币（1420 亿美元）的资本。此举将使银行增强支持经济的能力。彭博情报高级分析师 Francis Chan 分享了他的观点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-26/china-weighing-142b-capital-injection-into-top-banks-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 03:46:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国考虑向顶级银行注资 1420 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-26/china-weights-142b-capital-injection-into-top-banks-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社获悉，中国正考虑向其最大的国有银行注入 1 万亿元人民币或 1420 亿美元资本，以提高其放贷能力。彭博社中国通讯员 Minmin Low 与 Yvonne Man 和 David Ingles 在“彭博社：中国秀”节目中讨论了细节。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-26/china-weights-142b-capital-injection-into-top-banks-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 03:46:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>碧桂园债券持有人同意延期兑付人民币债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/country-garden-bondholders-approve-delays-on-yuan-bond-payments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，碧桂园控股有限公司已获得债券持有人的批准，将其九元人民币债券的偿付期限推迟六个月，从而使该开发商有更多时间规划境内债务重组。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/country-garden-bondholders-approve-delays-on-yuan-bond-payments</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 03:33:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>基本金属价格小幅下跌，因市场对中国刺激计划存疑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/base-metals-edge-lower-as-doubts-swirl-over-china-s-stimulus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者质疑中国本周早些时候出台的意外刺激计划是否能重振亚洲最大的经济体（包括房地产市场），基本金属和铁矿石价格下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/base-metals-edge-lower-as-doubts-swirl-over-china-s-stimulus</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 03:30:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国考虑向顶级银行注资 1420 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/china-weighs-injecting-142-billion-of-capital-into-top-banks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，中国正考虑向其最大的国有银行注入高达 1 万亿元人民币（1420 亿美元）的资本，以增强其支持陷入困境的经济的能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/china-weighs-injecting-142-billion-of-capital-into-top-banks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 01:56:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>有迹象显示利比亚可能很快恢复生产，油价持续大幅下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-sept-26</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于利比亚各派就欧佩克成员国央行领导权达成“妥协”，为恢复部分原油生产铺平了道路，油价在两周内最大跌幅之后趋于稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-sept-26</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 23:30:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
